            <title><![CDATA[Unreal Engine 6 announced with Rocket League reveal]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/unreal-engine-6-announced-with-rocket-league-reveal</link>
            <guid>1528870</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
        </ul>

    
    <p><span>A "new era" of Rocket League is on the way.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Psyonix revealed a “new era” of free-to-play vehicular soccer game <em>Rocket League</em> at <em>Rocket League</em> Championship Series 2026: Paris Major, which showcased the game running on Unreal Engine 6. <span id="more-1049789"></span></p><p>The teaser trailer marks the first reveal of the successor to Unreal Engine 5, which <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2020/05/unreal-engine-5-announced-with-ps5-tech-demo">first debuted</a> during the launch of the <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a> generation in 2020.</p><p><em>Rocket League</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, Mac, and Linux.</p><p>Watch the reveal trailer below.</p><h2><span><em>Rocket League</em> Unreal Engine 6 Reveal Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Rocket League® Reveal | Paris Major Crowd Reactions" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1ifIN2VWrmU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
        </div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/unreal-engine-6-announced-with-rocket-league-reveal]]></content:encoded>
